-- Mediobanca to take less than 1 bln euros of TLTRO funds - CEO
-- 
-- Wed Sep 17, 2014 09:57AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, Sept 17 (Reuters) - Mediobanca <MDBI.MI>, Italy's top investment bank, aims to draw less than 1 billion euros ($1.30 billion) from the funds the European Central Bank (ECB) is due to offer as part of a new long-term loan programme, its chief executive said on Wednesday.

